	<div id="title">
		<h1>ADMIN PANEL</h1>
		<h3>Keybinds</h3>
		<ul title="Keybinds">
			<li>Press <b>R</b> to refresh the page.</li>
			<li>Press <b>C</b> to filter by Authorized tweets.</li>
			<li>Press <b>B</b> to filter by Black listed tweets.</li>
			<li>Press <b>J</b> to go down.</li>
			<li>Press <b>K</b> to go up.</li>
			<li>Press <b>Y</b> to Authorize the selected tweet</li>
			<li>Press <b>N</b> to Black list the selected tweet</li>
			<li>Alternatively, you can just use your mouse (smh my head)</li>
		</ul>
